quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif Lam Ra. Awa ndi mavesi a Buku, ndipo ndi Korani yofotokoza bwino"
  15,2,Mwina iwo amene sakhulupirira adzafuna kuti akadakhala Asilamu
  15,3,"Alekeni kuti adye, ndi kuti asangalale ndipo alekeni kuti atangwanike ndi chikhulupiriro chabodza. Iwo adzadziwa posachedwapa"
  15,4,"Ndipo Ife sitinaonongepo mzinda wina uliwonse, kupatula pamene nthawi yake itakwana"
  15,5,Anthu sangathe kufulumizitsa chionongeko chawo kapena kuchichedwetsa ayi
  15,6,"Iwo amati, “Iwe, amene Korani yavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe! Ndithudi ndiwe munthu wa misala.”"
  15,7,“Bwanji siutibweretsera angelo ngati iweyo uli mmodzi mwa onena zoona?”
  15,8,"Ife sitimatsitsa pansi angelo, kupatula ndi choonadi ndipo zitatero iwo sadzapatsidwa nthawi"
  15,9,"Ndithudi ndife amene tidatsitsa Korani ndipo, ndithudi, Ife ndife amene tidzaiteteza"
  15,10,"Ndithudi Ife tidatumizapo, iwe usanadze, Atumwi ena pakati pa mibadwo yakale"
  15,11,"Ndipo sikunadze kwa iwo Mtumwi, amene iwo sanamuchite chipongwe"
  15,12,Kotero timalowetsa chisokonezo m’mitima ya anthu ochita zoipa
  15,13,Iwo sangakhulupirire mu uthenga wa Korani ndipo ndi chizolowezi cha anthu amene adalipo kale
  15,14,"Ndipo ngati Ife tikadatsekula khomo lakumwamba, iwo ndi kumakwera kumwamba mosalekeza"
  15,15,"Iwo akadakanabe kuti, “Maso athu athobwa. Ndithudi ife talodzedwa.”"
  15,16,Ndithudi Ife taika nyenyezi zikuluzikulu kumwamba ndipo tazikongoletsa kuti zizikondweretsa anthu oyang’ana
  15,17,Ndipo tawateteza malo a kumwamba kwa Satana wotembereredwa
  15,18,"Kupatula iye amene amamvetsera mwakuba, iye amatsatiridwa ndi malawi a moto"
  15,19,Ife tidatambasula dziko lapansi ndi kuikamo mapiri ndipo tameletsa mu ilo zinthu zosiyanasiyana chilichonse chili ndi muyeso wake
  15,20,Ndipo takupatsani mu ilo njira zopezela chakudya chanu ndi cha izo zimene inu simungathe kuzidyetsa
  15,21,"Palibe chilichonse, chimene nkhokwe yake siili ndi Ife ndipo sititumiza kupatula m’muyeso wodziwika"
  15,22,Ndipo Ife timatumiza mphepo yobereketsa ndipo timatsitsa madzi kuchokera kumwamba ndipo timakupatsani kuti mumwe; ndipo inu si ndinu osunga nkhokwe zake
  15,23,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife ndife amene timapereka moyo ndi imfa ndipo zinthu zonse ndi zathu"
  15,24,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife timadziwa onse amene adalipo kale inu musanadze ndipo timadziwa mibadwo yanu yatsopano ndi iwo amene adzadza m’tsogolo"
  15,25,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ambuye wako adzasonkhanitsa onse pamodzi. Zoonadi Iye ndi Wanzeru ndi Wodziwa chilichonse"
  15,26,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidamulenga munthu kuchokera ku dothi lotulutsa mawu, losinthidwa m’matope akuda osalala"
  15,27,Tidapanga mtundu wa majini poyamba kuchokera ku mphepo ya moto
  15,28,"Ndipo pamene Ambuye wako adati kwa angelo, “Ine ndilenga munthu kuchokera ku dothi lotulutsa mawu losinthidwa matope akuda osalala.”"
  15,29,“Motero ndikatha kumukonza ndi kuuzira mpweya umene ndidalenga chifukwa cha iye ndipo nonse gwadani kumulambira iye.”
  15,30,Motero Angelo onse adagwada ndi kumulambira
  15,31,Kupatula Satanaadakanakukhalammodzimwaolambira
  15,32,"Mulungu adati, “oh iwe Satana! Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani siuli pamodzi ndi olambira?”"
  15,33,"Satana adati, “Ine sindingagwadire munthu amene Inu mwamulenga kuchokera ku dothi lotulutsa mawu losinthidwa matope akuda osalala.”"
  15,34,"Mulungu adati: “Motero choka kuno chifukwa ndithudi iwe ndiwe wotembereredwa.”"
  15,35,"Ndipo, ndithudi, temberero lidzakhala pa iwe mpaka pa tsiku lachiweruzo.”"
  15,36,"Satana adati, “oh Ambuye wanga! Bandisungani mpaka patsiku louka kwa akufa.”"
  15,37,"Mulungu adati, “Ndithudi iwe uli m’gulu la anthu amene apatsidwa nthawi.”"
  15,38,“Mpaka pa nthawi ya tsiku lotsimikizika.”
  15,39,"Satana adati, “Oh Ambuye wanga! Popeza Inuyo mwandisocheretsa ine, ndithudi, ndidzawasalalitsira njira yautchimo anthu onse padziko lapansi, ndithudi onse ndidzawasocheretsa"
  15,40,Kupatula akapolo anu osankhidwa amene ali pakati pawo.”
  15,41,"Mulungu adati, “Imeneyi ndiyo njira imene idzalondola mwachindunji kwa Ine.”"
  15,42,"“Ndithudi iwe siudzakhala ndi mphamvu pa akapolo anga, kupatula anthu ochita zoipa amene amakutsatira iweyo.”"
  15,43,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, Gahena ndi malo olonjezedwa kwa iwo onse.”"
  15,44,"“Iyo ili ndi makomo asanu ndi awiri, ndipo chipata chilichonse chidzakhala ndi anthu ake olowapo.”"
  15,45,“Ndithudi! Onse oopa Mulungu adzakhala m’kati mwa minda ndi m’kati mwa a kasupe.”
  15,46,“Lowanimo mwamtendere mopanda mavuto.”
  15,47,“Ndipo Ife tidzachotsa m’mitima yawo mkwiyo uliwonse kuti akhoza kukhala pachibale ndi kupumula m’mipando yawofowofo moyang’anizana.”
  15,48,“Ndipo iwo sadzatopa kumeneko ndipo sadzafunsidwa kuti achoke ku Paradiso.”
  15,49,Auze akapolo anga kuti ndithudi Ine ndimakhululukira ndipo ndine wachisoni